街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為一入地鐵站就會生不如死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"我都係⋯冬天著衫唔會著到個人暖咁出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab611ed5944a5c9d848740d53095e1208c02c1a","tid":902623,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"一做運動仲痕得勁，手腳又紅曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有左依加幾年以為會自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc636aa512ffdaa5c409bf2ed53309ecfdcde8b","tid":902623,"uid":64401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"一熱就好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，比起熱唔鐘意焗"},{"pid":"810b84d4e0e6aa92b5b771dd95be3d153252686c","tid":902623,"uid":51566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8da944dc249f6a179d9bbf36219a06e63680ee1f","tid":902623,"uid":122511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"search下蕁麻疹/ 膽鹼能性蕁麻疹。<br />\n如果症狀大致都差唔多，搵個皮膚科睇吓<br />\n到時食佢地開既抗組胺藥就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個病, 最嚴重係廿十頭果陣<br />\n冬天行出街熱/焗少少, 會全身起哂紅色一粒粒上黎<br />\n好似起紅色既雞皮咁,不過痛到全身被針吉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾有KEEP 住做運動就會好返好多"},{"pid":"3048b4c66c16302355997db46183ae37afb23425","tid":902623,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45a895fac3ac7840173035ac13661801fd32d2a2","tid":902623,"uid":76681,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"俾針拮咁 只在冬天出現。<br />\n1. 一緊張就會突然發熱，即時比針吉<br />\n2. 由凍地方入去暖地方, 即出事( EG, 入MTR 車廂,入去暖既屋)<br />\n3. 通常會對陽光 / 燈 敏感  一曬,照射就針吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24698fd27de5b353618edd5d84ee9e35156cbb06","tid":902623,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"成身發滾然後鳩痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cb1a5bdace2b1411cd0586bc896871f3c3e583","tid":902623,"uid":144529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"好似比針吉咁？多數係頭痕先，之後先到個身"},{"pid":"1357e529fc261ce43871fdf42d40e0e6b8a9a46a","tid":902623,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"早幾年特別嚴重 同壓力有關<br />\n總之冬天一熱同焗就仆街<br />\n最嚴重個陣全個人都出紅色一點點<br />\n個陣睇西醫無效 再睇左幾個中醫<br />\n玩左兩三個月一樣係廢<br />\n之後搵到個西醫 食完有改善 不過一樣會發<br />\n最後搵到個醫到九成嘅方法<br />\n就係飲凍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好以為我講笑 個陣真係日日飲好多好多凍水<br />\n就無發得咁勁咁密 但真係要狂飲狂痾尿<br />\n咁就無事 咩藥都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf15a661f27bb496fed81a55cbe4e52dc0b5e37d","tid":902623,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"瘋狂做運動做到流曬汗就ok<br />\n每個星期一次<br />\n<br />\n過來人"},{"pid":"548c8106c0be743111ea9d90ab6885038a579fcc","tid":902623,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aaa3c408dd8ce5139ad87f871fc97994b724148","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"778fa44d9014e36d3a3b85eafc0be16152e54adf","tid":902623,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc8430e071ba22c0962d91b8ca16038b2edad2c8","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"通常都係做完運動後就會唔痕，但好快又會痕返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"做得唔夠？係咪出好多汗先？出汗係另一個改善血液循環的方法。<br />\n我以前超級鍾意冬天，因為我都係熱就痕。但自從成日做運動，宜家好怕凍。反而鍾意咗夏天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"你幾耐做一次運動？我一星期兩次每次跑30mins噉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"每日一至兩次左右，每次30min"},{"pid":"ff5a195a30478c76f2f06a9cf7482bdfe940665b","tid":902623,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"早幾年都係咁，辛苦到想死，之後多做運動出多啲汗，就無呢個情況。"},{"pid":"dcfa68c3c77101d496483af00f3d8f0e761ae8d6","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"點解你哋做運動得但我就無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9bf40c7691cb7bd583f9978700877a13b434c8","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a3e749069ad4be91ec9f17f79fb45fd5c6b07","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e598c4c8c875a3c591850a36d9ed28a674bae2","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d759117447de06f0f495ca6c80cd9b1722d5db","tid":902623,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}